title: Jordan's envoy to UN discusses arms embargo on Yemen rebels
description: The UN Security Council has passed a resolution on Yemen, imposing an arms embargo on the Houthi rebels. Dina Kawar, the president of the Security Council and Jordan's envoy to the UN, talks to Al Jazeera.
